import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.hist(data['delay'], bins=20, edgecolor='black')
    plt.xlabel('Delay Time')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of delay time?')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
        plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    avg_distance = data['distance'].mean()
    data['average_distance'] = avg_distance
    
    ax = data['average_distance'].plot(kind='bar')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.axhline(avg_distance, color='r', linestyle='--', label=f'Average Distance: {avg_distance:.2f}')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title("What is the average distance traveled by flights?", wrap=True)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd

import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    day_counts = data['day_of_week'].value_counts()
    day_counts.plot(kind='bar')
    
    plt.xlabel('Day of the Week')
    plt.ylabel('Number of Flights')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of flights by day of the week?')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    heatmap_data = data.groupby(['origin', 'destination']).size().unstack()
    plt.imshow(heatmap_data, cmap='viridis')
    plt.xticks(range(len(heatmap_data.columns)), heatmap_data.columns, rotation=90)
    plt.yticks(range(len(heatmap_data.index)), heatmap_data.index)
    plt.xlabel('Destination')
    plt.ylabel('Origin')
    plt.colorbar(label='Number of Flights')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of flights by origin and destination?', wrap=True)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
